cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically emotion cause extraction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a deep learning framework for the task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the task of emotion cause extraction can be seen as a form of information retrieval from text. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on evolutionary computing, but it is still possible as the paper proposes a neural network-based approach.
